{
  "texts": [
    "Consequently, it is crucial for GPT programs to demonstrate accuracy to fulfill their intended functions for image diagnosis in dental medicine effectively.",
    "A search for panoramic radiographs was conducted on the open-access websites Radiopaedia.org (https://radiopae- dia.org/) and CDI Peru (https://cdi.com.pe/), which provide well-documented clinical cases.",
    "The inclusion criteria were clinical cases with panoramic radiographs displaying permanent dentition and a single radiolucent lesion in the maxilla or mandible, with histopathological confirmation or a probable differential diagnosis, and presenting specific hyperlinks that redirected to the corresponding isolated panoramic radiograph (i.e., not the full webpage with textual information).",
    "Blurry, cropped, or edited panoramic radiographs containing annotations such as arrows, circles, lines, or texts were not included in this study.",
    "This resulted in a total of 28 panoramic radiographs included for further analysis (Annex 1)."
  ]
}